Package: dashboard-shakhsi
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, gir1.2-webkit2-4.1 | gir1.2-webkit2-4.0
Installed-Size: @SIZE@
Maintainer: Dashboard User <user@localhost>
Description: Personal dashboard with tasks and finance tracking (Persian)
 Liquid-glass style personal dashboard: task manager with priorities
 and filters, plus finance tracking (income, expenses, debts,
 installments) with Jalali calendar and charts.
 All data persists locally in ~/.local/share/dashboard-shakhsi/.
